iler": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "WR_V5_Store_Quest_Video_Thumbnail.png", "id": "1115066816204493", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75272215_1115066819537826_2999547195316242706_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=AiQH3Ph7AssQ7kNvgG2HZpc&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA3jTP5v1dujo_gCf63P68_jslfrjijSEpYegK6NVhfuA&oe=66FE9291"}, "display_name": "WHITEROOM", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Making metaverse deployment safe and simple for enterprises\n\nWHITEROOM is a metaverse platform designed for enterprises that supports both VR (virtual reality) and MR (mixed reality).\n\nIt supports multi-devices, multimedia, and multi-users, so you can participate in meetings as an avatar from any location and on any device as long as there is a network environment. You can communicate while sharing 3D models, office documents, PDFs, images, videos, etc. in the Metaverse space.\n\nBy supporting both VR and MR, it is possible to establish a real contact point in the metaverse space, enabling new communication that connects the field and the office.", "short_description": "Making metaverse deployment safe and simple for enterprises"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "CoverImageSafeAreaTemplatePortrait.png", "id": "5310090842368585", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031484_5310090845701918_1084593935181500038_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=DbSZslFfoIEQ7kNvgF_HlrU&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAcC5o9GjI9anEhrhuegQCbjyaIHdU_bDvlhR3AeMb2IQ&oe=66FE9F8E"}, {"file_name": "CoverImageSafeAreaTemplateSquare.png", "id": "1189446091593130", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982665_1189446094926463_7411146096846439131_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=1zMPopII3wUQ7kNvgGFIZt-&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAcVOFlbbmW0rpRWXOpuJgSiOhzJKeQ7dpwZk7l5V9xvg&oe=66FE780